cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "rnaseq2tracks"
version: "3.0"
date-released: "2026-05-13"
abstract: >
  End-to-end RNA-seq workflow from raw FASTQ to count matrices,
  DESeq2-normalized BigWig tracks, and differential expression results.
  Supports single-end and paired-end libraries, strand-specific coverage,
  and UCSC-compatible BigWig output for human and mouse genomes.
authors:
